# Medical Classification Tool

A Gradio-based AI tool for medical image classification and disease text analysis.

![Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-HuggingFace_Spaces-blue) 
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)

## Features

- **Image Classification**: Analyze medical images (X-rays, CT scans) using Vision Transformer (ViT)
- **Text Analysis**: Detect disease mentions in clinical text using BioBERT/NER models

## How to Use

1. **Image Classification Tab**:
   - Upload any medical image (JPEG/PNG)
   - Get AI-powered classification results

2. **Text Analysis Tab**:
   - Enter medical text (symptoms, clinical notes)
   - Receive disease entity recognition results

## Deployment

### Local Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/medical-ai.git
cd medical-ai
pip install -r requirements.txt
python doctor.py